so to find the starting of the loop
we can take two pointer `p1` and `p2`

 `p1` will point to head of linked list
 `p2` will point to node `k`

 and then we can just iterate till `p1` and `p2` not become equal
 and once they become equal the 
	 pointer `p1` will have travelled `m`distance
	 and pointer `p2` will have travelled `d` distance

and this point will be the starting of the loop `s`

